deck: Spike and the others are magically transported into his comic, where in order for them to leave they must stop the evil Mane-iac.
description:
While Twilight and her friends clean up Celestia and Luna's old castle, Spike feeling left out and not needed goes to read the rest of his comic until he comes to a blank page with a little inscription in the bottom corner. After using a magnifying glass to read it Spike and the others are transported to the city to Maretropolis where they become the "Power Ponies" and spike becomes their sidekick "Humdrum". Spike then tells them in order for them to return home they must stop the Mane-iac.

Points of Interest

This episode and the powers the mane six obtain in the episodes are heavenly based off characters from the DC/Marvel franchises.
